#

Carrot and Cucumber Salad

10 min
$5
80 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickRefreshing

Description

A refreshing and crunchy salad that's perfect for a light meal or side dish!

Ingredients

  • carrots: 2 large, grated
  • cucumber: 1 large, diced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped (optional)
